6 bedroom villa in San Klang, San Pa Tong, for sale. The expansive single story home is built on 954 wah of land with garden, large pool (10 by 4.5 meters), and office/guest area in the rear of the property.

The main house is built into two wings, with the three bedrooms in the right wing and a large recreation room, dining room, kitchen, and bar in the other. The living room and entrance to the large patio is in the middle of the two wings. The entire property has a simple and very light and open design letting in plenty of light.

The master bedroom has a direct entrance onto the patio, a sitting area, and large en suite bathroom. The other two guest bedrooms in the main house also have en suite bathrooms and one has a private terrace.
